1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:08,000
Hi, I'm the SAP Specialist. I made La Piazza, the town square for you. Let me show you around.

2
00:00:08,000 --> 00:00:14,000
This is your town square — your neighbours' stuff to borrow, learn, sell and help with.

3
00:00:14,000 --> 00:00:20,000
No fees, no middlemen, nobody selling your data. Sign up in one motion.

4
00:00:20,000 --> 00:00:26,000
Just tell the machine who you are — a simple sentence or two. No CVs, no forms.

5
00:00:26,000 --> 00:00:36,000
La Piazza builds your own workshop, tailored to you — your bio, your skills — in about 30 seconds.

6
00:00:36,000 --> 00:00:43,000
Boom — you're a member. It even nudges you to add a photo. No fees, you're in.

7
00:00:43,000 --> 00:00:52,000
And here's your workshop, your Bottega — make a poster, ask a master, find your edge. This is yours, right away.

8
00:00:52,000 --> 00:00:59,000
Next episode — watch Mike ask the whole town to move his garage. Subscribe and learn more.

9
00:00:59,000 --> 00:01:03,000
A presto. See you soon.
